	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64696030"><p>This so fits the stereotype of what most people think of cybersecurity: "security == inconvenience"</p><p>The fact that supposed security experts would think so lightly of a piece of security software bringing down the systems it was supposed to protect shows how abyssal the state of the industry is.  Availability was supposed to be one of the aim of security, and that seemed to be lost somewhere in all the buzzwords.</p></div>
	</div>

