		<div id="comment_body_64696538">What's needed is a <a href="http://large.stanford.edu/courses/2012/ph240/lee2/" title="stanford.edu">Manhattan Project</a> [stanford.edu]. To design a platform that can't be compromised by feeding it a amalicous script or opening an email attachment or clicking on a malicous WebLink.<br> <br>

The WinTEL model obviously showing its age and despite masses of sticking-plaster such as CrowdStrike, can never measure up to the task. Since a lot of peoples jobs depend on not knowing this - nothing is going to change.</div>
